title: Harry Gunnarsson
text: Harry Gunnarsson (9 September 1929 – 22 March 2012) was a Swedish <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201952%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Welterweight">men's welterweight</a> event at the <a href="1952%20Summer%20Olympics">1952 Summer Olympics</a>.
